---
const pricing = [
  { tier: 'Standard Planning', fee: '$100 / case', nobel: '$75 / case', notes: 'Single case, 48–72 hour turnaround' },
  { tier: 'Volume Planning (10+ / month)', fee: '$85 / case', nobel: '$60 / case', notes: 'For active labs and multi-provider groups' },
  { tier: 'Expedited Add-On (24 hour)', fee: '+$50', nobel: '+$40', notes: 'Rush fee added to selected base tier' },
];
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Surgical Guide Planning Services | RMDI</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #f7fafc; color: #1f2937; }
      .wrap { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 20px; }
      .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.05); }
      h1,h2 { margin: 0 0 12px; }
      table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
      th, td { text-align: left; padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
      th { background: #eff6ff; }
      .badge { display:inline-block; background:#dcfce7; color:#166534; padding:6px 10px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:700; }
      .cta { background:#1d4ed8; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:8px; display:inline-block; }
      .small { font-size: .92rem; color:#4b5563; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="card">
        <h1>Surgical Guide Planning Services</h1>
        <p>Remote implant planning support for labs and restoring doctors. Built for real-world workflows: DICOM + STL intake, plan review, and STL handoff for guide fabrication.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Pricing</h2>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Service Tier</th>
              <th>Standard Fee</th>
              <th>Nobel Customer Discount</th>
              <th>Details</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {pricing.map((row) => (
              <tr>
                <td>{row.tier}</td>
                <td>{row.fee}</td>
                <td>{row.nobel}</td>
                <td>{row.notes}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="small" style="margin-top:10px;">Nobel customer discount applies to active Nobel accounts and approved partner labs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Pilot Offer for Current Nobel Territory Accounts</h2>
        <p><span class="badge">$0 Planning Fee</span></p>
        <p>For current Nobel accounts in Joe Casey’s active territory, planning services are currently provided at <strong>no charge</strong> during pilot testing and workflow validation.</p>
        <p class="small">Guide manufacturing/fabrication costs are separate and handled by the lab.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>What’s Included</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>DICOM + STL review</li>
          <li>Implant position planning support</li>
          <li>Virtual case review call</li>
          <li>STL export handoff for lab fabrication</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="cta" href="mailto:info@rockymountaindentalimplants.com?subject=RMDI%20Surgical%20Guide%20Planning%20Pilot">Start Partner Pilot</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
